metadata.title: Salmonid Enhancement Program (Canada)

creators.name: Oceans Canada, Science Branch - Data Analyst

metadata.description:
Parameter
Biological data sampled from adult and jack hatchery reared salmonids

Measurement Details
Data collected are site and species dependant, but include lengths, sex, weight, age, coded wire tags, adipose fin clips, scales and otoliths.

Coastal British Columbia

[ A TCODE project ]
